                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with a previous con<lb></lb>viction at Clerkenwell in July</hi>, 1871., <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">
